Text:
Quality good but Dulph Lundgren yuk! Wouldn't have dl'd it if I knew, but thought maybe he's improved might as well give it a chance, wish I hadn't. 

No plot rubbish acting. A chase movie with loads of shooting and blowing shit up. Total crap from beginning to end and insult to ones intelligence. Straight to the bin for this waste of a carbon footprint. I feel all dirty now!
You might not like Dolph Lundgren, but i do. Everytime Dolph is in a movie, i know it is going to be an exciting action movie, so you have nothing to complain about...
